# Foundry
# contracts/out/ is mostly throwaway dependency artifacts (OpenZeppelin,
# forge-std, etc.). We commit only the two ABIs the @sovereignclaw/inft
# tsup build inlines, so CI/Railway builds don't need Foundry installed.
# Local rebuild via `pnpm contracts:build` keeps everything fresh.
contracts/out/*
!contracts/out/AgentNFT.sol/
!contracts/out/MemoryRevocation.sol/
contracts/out/AgentNFT.sol/*
contracts/out/MemoryRevocation.sol/*
!contracts/out/AgentNFT.sol/AgentNFT.json
!contracts/out/MemoryRevocation.sol/MemoryRevocation.json
contracts/cache/
contracts/broadcast/
contracts/lib/

# IDE
.vscode/*
!.vscode/settings.json
.idea/